				%h4 From Hongdae Station, take AREX back to ICN			
				%p Hop in a cab for a short ride to Hongdae Station, exit 4, to catch the rail back to the airport. Give yourself an hour to arrive at the airport. If you want to rush, you can leave as late as 3:30 p.m., but arriving early will give you plenty of time to check in, take much-needed showers (details below) and unwind for a change.
